rem ====================
rem  ﾛｸﾞ出力開始
rem ====================
SetLogStream objWriteLogStream, True
SendLog WScript.ScriptName & "を開始しました"

rem ====================
rem  step1
rem ====================
rem workフォルダの作成
if (objFileSys.FolderExists(pathWork2))  Then
  objFileSys.DeleteFolder pathWork2, True
end if
